headline: Q3 Earnings Roundup: A. O. Smith (NYSE:AOS) And The Rest Of The HVAC and Water Systems Segment
summary: Quarterly earnings results are a good time to check in on a company’s progress, especially compared to its peers in the same sector. Today we are looking at A. O. Smith (NYSE:AOS) and the best and worst performers in the hvac and water systems industry.
